# Overrides CONFIG.WEBSITE_URL (default: https://www.pokebrowser.net). Set this
# to test the extension against a locally running web app:
VITE_WEBSITE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Optional — only needed to point the extension at a different Supabase
# project than the committed default (see extension/src/lib/config.ts).
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
